					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody"><div class="quotetitle">Celius wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">I was considering using MMC3, but I don't quite understand how it works. I've worked a little with it before, and I made a scrolling demo with all the code in $8000-$BFFF. When I tried again with all the code in $C000-$FFFF, the code worked in every emulator except Nintendulator. I don't understand how the banking works in MMC3.</div>
<br />The banks in $8000, $A000, and $C000 are not specified at startup. Your init code should be in $E000-$FFFF, writing to $8000 and $8001 to set up these banks before you jump there.</div>

